						               													<description>Abaddon: Shattered Command is an expansion for Richard Borg's Abaddon. The expansion adds a new unit, Command Bunker. These immobile fortresses are extremely potent in defense, but have no offensive capability. They provide support to all of your units through the Program Deck. Each Program card adds powerful abilities to affect the battlefield.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In addition to the Command Bunker, unit upgrades have been added. Now your Link or Infantry can be equipped with modified weapons, jump packs, or improved targeting systems.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Also included is a point system for building your own battles, want to fight 8 heavy Links against a horde of infantry? Now you can build that battle.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Terrain rules have been added as well, now terrain can be entered and it can provide bonuses for the occupants.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Finally eight additional scenarios are included. These scenarios feature the rules added in the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Included in this expansion:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;16 page Rule book-Scenario Book&amp;#10;&amp;#10;3 Tile Sheets (Command Bunkers, Terrain, Power Crytstals and Upgrade Markers.)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;2 reference sheets&amp;#10;&amp;#10;20 card Program Deck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
